1 KeePass Integration			1	1_Heading.0	Not relevant		
	Requirements for connecting to a local KeePass 4.x database to retrieve credentials used by integrations.	information	1.1	PO-KP-INFO-001.0	Not relevant		
1.1 KeePass Requirements			1.1	1_1_Heading.0	Not relevant		
	The system shall connect to a local KeePass 4.x KDBX database file using the pykeepass library.	functional requirement	1.1.1	PO-KP-001.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
	The KeePass integration shall support unlocking the database via master password and/or key file.	functional requirement	1.1.2	PO-KP-002.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
	The system shall support retrieving credentials from the KeePass database by entry name or entry path.	functional requirement	1.1.3	PO-KP-003.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
	The KeePass database shall be automatically locked after a configurable idle timeout.	functional requirement	1.1.4	PO-KP-004.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
	The KeePass database file path shall be saved in QSettings via the SettingsManager and selectable from the KeePass Configuration dialog.	functional requirement	1.1.5	PO-KP-005.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
	Sensitive information (master password, key file content) shall never be written to log files, debug dumps, or settings files.	functional requirement	1.1.6	PO-KP-006.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
</OBJECTS>
